<h3>What does it do?</h3>
<div class="rmc">
<h4>FREE Mobile Motoring App</h4>
<p>To keep you in the driving seat, the Mobile Motoring App for iPhone lets Brand Car Insurance customers tap into help in an emergency on the road.</p>
<p>The full functionality of the App is available to Brand Car Insurance customers who bought a policy on or after 16 October 2010 or renewed on or after 12 November 2010. Full terms of use can be found on the application.</p>
<h4>Help in the event of an accident</h4>
<p>If you're involved in a car accident, it's not always easy to think straight. The Mobile Motoring App gives Brand Bank Car Insurance customers on-the-spot tips and helps you gather all the key details, step by step. You can call the claims team, or, you can use the App to record and store the information and e-mail the claims team who will call you back within 24 hours.</p>
<h4>Tap into a bit of calm in a crisis</h4>
<p>Being involved in an accident can be very stressful. If you're not sure what to do, we'll steer you in the right direction with quick tips and guidance.</p>
<h4>Step-by-step help</h4>
<p>The App will take you through certain info you need to collect - like details of the incident, and other drivers and witnesses. Mobile Motoring can save it all as you go.</p>
<h4>It's easy to use</h4>
<p>Mobile Motoring provides an easy and convenient way to record and store all the key details, including photos. Then to start your claim - just tap send.</p>
<h4>Submit Claims</h4>
<p>Once you have sent the details of the incident, a member of the claims team will call you within 24 hours and they'll aim to make sure they get you back on the road as quickly as possible.</p>
<h4>Help if your car breaks down</h4>
<p>Mobile Motoring to the rescue!</p>
<p>If your car breaks down, with Mobile Motoring help can soon be on its way. As well as useful breakdown tips and assistance, the app pinpoints your exact location using the GPS signal.</p>
<h4>Help with important reminders</h4>
<p>Using your iPhone calendar, Mobile Motoring will give you timely reminders for your MOT/Service, road tax and car insurance.</p>
<h4>Insurance quotes</h4>
<p>Mobile Motoring can direct you to quality cover at a Brand Price.</p>
<p>Mobile Motoring could help you save on a range of insurances. You can use the app to link to the Brand Bank website to get quotes and apply for cover.</p>
<p>Download the Mobile Motoring app at <a shape="rect" rel="external" href="http://www.apple.com/uk">www.apple.com/uk</a>.</p>
